                    <div class="col">
                        <p>The ShaniDoshaNivaranaPooja is used to remove the Shani/Saturn dosha and to achieve the Rajayoga
                             through the absolute sanction of Shani. This Pooja proves to be very beneficial when the Saturn
                              is afflicted in the horoscope. During the depression time the ShaniYantrais very useful. This
                               Pooja indicates the success in the personal life as well as in the professional life. The Pooja
                                is basically performed to achieve blessings of Lord Shani and to justify the shanidosha. The
                                 position of Shani in the specific house of the natal horoscope causes problem to the natives.
                                  The effect of Shani is very low as it is a very slow moving planet. 
                        </p>
                        
                        
